{"Sid":0,"Did":118122,"Id":"282270","Title":"礁溪成功新村武聖廟","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/00b4e28e-937f-4d17-86cf-18b9f4b04a82/108-her-pa-1805-201910252205255db2e16a5063c0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n大陳島撤退居民所形成的移民聚落礁溪成功新村，其宗教信仰中心為武聖宮。武聖宮主神神向金面關帝爺神像與華陀神像、佛帳乃自大陳原鄉攜來，原安奉在大禮堂中。但1991年2月因孩童玩火導致的火災將大禮堂與神像燒毀，促使居民倡議在大禮堂原址新建武聖廟。 　　武聖廟在1993年11月18日舉行開光落成大典暨華陀祖師聖誕，廟名沿用大陳原鄉原廟名－武聖廟，廟內擺設完全仿造大陳島武聖廟。此外，大陳撤退時僅攜帶2尊神像來台，武聖廟新建後，將原鄉武聖廟內原來所有神像全部重塑補齊。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.768084","Keyword_Latitude":"24.8282058","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/BD62921F-8CE2-4403-9244-909E6B308BB0","Original_Identifier":"282270","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"大陳 / 成功新村 / 礁溪 / 關聖帝君 / 關聖廟","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:09:35","timelines":"","place":"礁溪鄉成功新村","address":"宜蘭縣礁溪鄉成功路32之2號","longitude":"121.768084","latitude":"24.8282058","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"林世傑/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/63b5d656-4779-4fca-b01e-8f7414853601/108-her-pa-1805-re-201910252207385db2e16a5063c0.jpg"}}